{"tid":2094042,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"首位秘密警察一姐 劉賜蕙權大無制衡  泛民憂國安處變超級東廠","createTime":"2020-07-04T09:31:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T11:59:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"93a14d05045a52fb9e9c951d2a6cb65404cf848f","tid":2094042,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T09:31:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200704/KQED4J2HEPHXVAZTM6LOXTOLFE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200704%2FKQED4J2HEPHXVAZTM6LOXTOLFE%2F&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmseYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=7170bfb6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200704%2FKQED4J2HEPHXVAZTM6LOXTOLFE%2F&h=cda078ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200704/KQED4J2HEPHXVAZTM6LOXTOLFE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n首位秘密警察一姐 劉賜蕙權大無制衡 <br />\n泛民憂國安處變超級東廠<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/IXbiJ5xaoOz5KoBx0CTC1gXg8vw=/499x341/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/U5NHL6GTEWUPY636EHD4OPNMWU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIXbiJ5xaoOz5KoBx0CTC1gXg8vw%3D%2F499x341%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FU5NHL6GTEWUPY636EHD4OPNMWU.gif&h=345cda7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥昨任命劉賜蕙為警務處副處長（國家安全），即日宣誓就任。政府新聞處圖片<br />\n<br />\n【兩制蓋棺】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府宣佈按港區國安法<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n將變成權力無限大的「超級東廠」。<br />\n<br />\n政府昨公佈，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n承擔維護國家安全的重責。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：被告多處骨折缺席聆訊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可調動飛虎隊<br />\n<br />\n54歲的劉賜蕙<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n警隊歷來第二名女副處長。<br />\n<br />\n政府並無交代新設的警務處<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n軍械法證課等人手配合。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n撥款毋須審批<br />\n<br />\n李家超<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n目標人物入境。<br />\n<br />\n劉賜蕙出任新增的警務處副處長（國家安全）職位，每月薪酬24.3萬至25.8萬元，加薪一成多。另外，國安處初期會有150至200名人手，來自警隊不同部門，人手未來會再增加。李家超表示，不排除會招募退休警務人員及其他紀律部隊人員加入國安處。由於港區國安法規定，財政司長從政府一般收入中，撥出專門款項支付維護國家安全開支及核准人員編制，不受本港現行法律規定限制，所以國安處成立毋須經立法會撥款審批。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員林卓廷指出，國安處編制不受監管，日後行動亦「冇王管」，竊聽更加毋須事先申請，令人擔心會變成權力無限大的「超級東廠」，市民的人權自由都受威脅，近日黃店在警方威嚇下要急急清除文宣，顯示社會上已出現寒蟬效應。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/oOBHJWIEVwrP6o8BaUs-43xuiis=/499x319/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/33VD4SIMN4WGP2XQJFPKDFQ4OI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FoOBHJWIEVwrP6o8BaUs-43xuiis%3D%2F499x319%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F33VD4SIMN4WGP2XQJFPKDFQ4OI.gif&h=2943423b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n7.1當日，警務處國家安全處人員執勤時掛上N字頭粉紅呼號卡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lqkk-M4nVQgnCx_v9cnZK71QVeQ=/499x330/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CYZYON6DBOSNOTLZSFSAGHANVE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Flqkk-M4nVQgnCx_v9cnZK71QVeQ%3D%2F499x330%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCYZYON6DBOSNOTLZSFSAGHANVE.gif&h=79a6b199&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國安處在警隊濫暴爭議聲中成立，行動不受監管，恐變成權力無限大的「超級東廠」。"},{"pid":"85479f8c9c9044e24401ad11cb83169cd077a77f","tid":2094042,"uid":165881,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T09:39:47.000Z","msg":"歷史不斷重複，東廠，西廠返黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16e93811507bb21671358110cf11d17095de4752","tid":2094042,"uid":267647,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T09:47:22.000Z","msg":"仲惡過警務處處長"},{"pid":"afe335eada83e9cce1719a35b751a56a70efb407","tid":2094042,"uid":33471,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T09:59:43.000Z","msg":"柒婆上位整咁多手袋黨"},{"pid":"aa0d91cdf13b6a96c6832ac5